Package com.behreajj.camzup.core

Class Entity3

java.lang.Object
com.behreajj.camzup.core.Entity
com.behreajj.camzup.core.Entity3
All Implemented Interfaces:
IOriented3, ISpatial3, Comparable<Entity3>
Direct Known Subclasses:
CamEntity3, CurveEntity3, MeshEntity3
public class Entity3 extends Entity implements Comparable<Entity3>, IOriented3, ISpatial3
An entity in three-dimensional space that can be moved around with a transform, but contains no other data. Useful when a 'target' entity is needed.
